{"tid":600291,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"(黃子華效應?) 曾志偉再拍賀歲片, 會用全廣東話拍","createTime":"2018-03-21T07:34:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-22T09:44:16.000Z","uid":134071,"like":4,"dislike":68,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"c8950519ee9f1e35a9adbaf6b281741ab0d39a50","tid":600291,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T07:34:11.000Z","msg":"見到&quot;棟篤特工&quot;香港咁收得, 曾志偉又要落水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再為「娘家」效力　志偉預告全粵語拍賀歲片 (14:08)<br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=8RtZhivwEXyJ6g6JeIdj0Yzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=ca5595b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】導演劉偉強、曾志偉、王晶等到灣仔會展出席「邵氏兄弟電影發布會」，以「回娘家」形式現身支持。<br />\n<br />\n曾志偉以香港演藝界內地發展協會執行會長身份現身，他表示：「邵氏對香港人充滿難能可貴嘅回憶，我自己都係邵氏培育73年加入邵氏做許冠文嘅替身，之後再喺TVB成長。近年我拍咗唔少賀歲片，新一年想繼續效力，拍一套以大灣區為對象嘅賀歲片，呢個地區有七千萬，加埋鄰近地區有一億人，會用全廣東話拍，希望演員冇包袱。」"},{"pid":"f3e1ab67b31c5c168383d28fd0e1517fea0546df","tid":600291,"uid":42848,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T07:36:52.000Z","msg":"拍一套以大灣區為對象嘅賀歲片，呢個地區有七千萬，加埋鄰近地區有一億人，會用全廣東話拍，希望演員冇包袱。<br />\n<br />\n米奇好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7b085857be2b4cb2d446c2dd363155f1de999bf","tid":600291,"uid":37666,"like":47,"dislike":4,"score":43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T07:41:05.000Z","msg":"收皮啦 成日扮支持香港<br />\n又拍得唔好笑 無啦啦又唱歌啲笑話又爛"},{"pid":"c8adf46d70a8b89d638b7269d8ec40d7a313b633","tid":600291,"uid":40470,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T07:41:59.000Z","msg":"之前單野有無人記得"},{"pid":"1733554a6b4a32aebcc8490fd122843bc0a61c7c","tid":600291,"uid":31961,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T07:42:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>藍</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"0e6f43bd23442979738a9